data.meta_description: Maxime Chaya | Lebanese mountaineer, explorer and sportsman⠀ ⠀ “There is an Everest for everyone.”⠀ ⠀ After winning a mountain bike race in Kenya, Chaya was invited to climb Mt Kilimanjaro in nearby Tanzania. He discovered his passion for mountaineering on the way up and decided to challenge himself further...⠀ ⠀ Over the next 3 years, Chaya completed the Seven Summits challenge, becoming the first Lebanese to climb Mt Everest in 2006.
